'''Turks in Kuwait''' ({{lang-tr|Kuveyt T√ºrkleri}}) are Kuwaiti people of Turkish ancestry and foreign [[Turkish people]] who live in [[Kuwait]]. By Turkish roots, this could mean roots linking back to [[Turkey]], the island of [[Cyprus]] or the communities of the [[Turkish diaspora]].
== History == {{Empty section|date=July 2010}} == Business == Turkish people works in barber shops, furniture shops, restaurants There are Turkish teachers, doctors, engineers and businessmen in Kuwait.
